Package io.nem.symbol.sdk.model.mosaic

Class NetworkCurrency

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.nem.symbol.sdk.model.mosaic.NetworkCurrency
  • public class NetworkCurrency
extends java.lang.Object
    This object holds the configuration of a given currency. The configuration can be provided by user (offline work) or loaded via rest (online work, currently using block/1 transaction).

    Some commonly used and known instances are also provided statically if the user wants to work offline.

    Objects of this class are created using the NetworkCurrencyBuilder and they are thread safe and immutable.

    See Also:
    NetworkCurrencyService, RepositoryFactory, RepositoryFactoryBase, NetworkCurrencyBuilder
